  Bug: BG channel becomes -1 as shown from monitor task output!
  Reason: In spCtrl, setting peerChanId to -1 is done AFTER splice indication
          is sent.  If another splice request is received, the peerChanId
          will be set, which will later be set to -1 in spCtrl.
  Solution: move peerChanId setting to before sending of splice indication.
            => dpi1183.fls from ytse-rel2_3dp, not checked in.



