  BUG: in new poll reset mechanism, pollCnt will only be increment when life
       is set.  As a result, without using the LIFE keyword, pollCnt will never
       get increment and reset mechanism will not work.


3/10/01
  New FG ready que overflow checking:
    Instead of using a fixed max que size, we can use the distance between
    top of queue DTS and current time.  In order to avoid statmux's scheduler
    running empty, we only need to gaurantee to send a frame no later than
    DTS-0.25 sec.
    For robustness, we still need to use a MAX_FG_QUEUE_SZ but set it to a
    very high number, like 20.  This can avoid problem if we have a bad DTS
    on top of queue.



