  Support of idleTime:
    In Splice Control Task, recompute CPU loading every 20*50ms = 1 sec.
    Idle % = (change in idle_cnt) / (interval * maxCPUload) * 100%
    interval = change in ticks * 10 msec = chagne in ticks / 100 (sec)

